official_title: Postpartum HPV Vaccination: Acceptability, Uptake and Immunogenicity
inclusion_criteria:
* postpartum day 0-4 after vaginal or Cesarean delivery at UAB hospital

Exclusion criteria

* Fetal demise or miscarriage, autoimmune disorder, HIV, Hepatitis B/C, chronic steroid use, preeclampsia, non-English speaking
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 16 Years
Must have maximum age of 26 Years
